com.gigya.socialize.android

Class GSPluginFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • android.support.v4.app.DialogFragment
        • com.gigya.socialize.android.GSPluginFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.DialogInterface.OnCancelListener, android.content.DialogInterface.OnDismissListener, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class GSPluginFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.DialogFragment

    GSPluginFragment is a custom fragment that renders Gigya JS Plugins and integrates them seamlessly with the Gigya Android SDK.

    GSPluginFragment currently supports the following plugins, listed with their pluginName:

    • Comments - comments.commentsUI
    • Reviews - comments.commentsUI
    • RaaS Screen-Sets - accounts.screenSet
